### Get activity feed for workspace
GET http://localhost:6767/activity?workspace=WORKSPACE_ID_HERE

###

### Get activity for a specific board
GET http://localhost:6767/activity?workspace=WORKSPACE_ID_HERE&entityType=Board&entityId=BOARD_ID_HERE

###

### Get activity for a specific card
GET http://localhost:6767/activity?workspace=WORKSPACE_ID_HERE&entityType=Card&entityId=CARD_ID_HERE

###

### Get my activity (what I did)
GET http://localhost:6767/activity/me
